data.description: Come see this beautiful, well maintained home.  It sits on just over one acre on a cul-de-sac among great mature trees.   Entertain with your custom pool, gazebo and large covered patio in summer or winter months.   There is a detached garage  with electricity and 30 amp plug for your RV hook up.  There is so much to this property that you'll need to see it to believe it.   Come see country living at its finest.
